{"tid":1507314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"員佐級協會：記者嚴重阻礙警方工作　「暴徒」武力升級促警重新檢視武力使用方案","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:40:11.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f56554c8480b5af61b769b51c3f3df972416b92","tid":1507314,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/69800668_10157295925581422_2690730537735159808_o_itLLm_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F69800668_10157295925581422_2690730537735159808_o_itLLm_1200x0.jpg&h=49da1327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日（25日）有人發起荃葵青大遊行，不過之後再次演變成激烈警民衝突，警方首次出動水炮車清場，晚上更有警員一度以手槍指向示威者及記者，警方事後證實有警員曾經開槍。警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉今日（26日）發表聲明，批評有記者忽視自身安全，經常逗留在警察防線與暴徒對峙區域之間，「此舉不但把記者的自身安全放到一個危險的地方，亦嚴重阻礙警方的工作」。林志偉嚴正呼籲各大傳媒機構記者，採訪時切勿在危險位置逗留，亦切勿阻礙警察工作。<br />\n<br />\n員佐級協會今日發表聲明，指在剛過去的週末，「暴徒」再度藉集會遊行集結，繼而在港九新界多區進行惡意破壞及製造事端。聲明指，每當警察出現平息混亂，「暴徒」隨即對警方使用「層出不窮，不斷升級的武力」，包括用燃燒彈、懷疑刀類利器、甚至「思疑槍械」攻擊警察。佐級協會表示，對於目無法紀的違法暴力及破壞行為，協會感到極度憤概，並予以嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n林志偉：警方武力明顯較低　促檢視以驅散為主策略<br />\n<br />\n林志偉又在聲明中表示，因應「暴徒」使用的武力不斷升級，不少更達到致命的程度，「相反警方只能以明顯較低的武力應對」，促請警隊管理層立即重新檢視現時以驅散為主的行動策略及武力使用方案。林志偉指，警員在執勤時的人生（身）安全保障正面臨前所未有的重大考驗，「管理層切勿坐視對此等威脅人員安全的情況！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/r-%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%90%E7%B4%9A%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%80%97%E7%95%99%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%BF%BD%E8%A6%96%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fr-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2590%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2580%2597%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=37c86996\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fr-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2590%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2580%2597%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259F%259F%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&h=256d8500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/r-%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%90%E7%B4%9A%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%80%97%E7%95%99%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E5%8D%80%E5%9F%9F%E5%BF%BD%E8%A6%96%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8-%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C/</a>"},{"pid":"ce04904af13cfb66fe574cd6f8933de8ca4f9406","tid":1507314,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=1405614b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"c7c52229491a6e032a7a3fa26af33eebed5b2b1d","tid":1507314,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白